<span id="freeTextContainer17335678492631575659">A good book Shattered lies has everything adultery secrets lies race etc.<br/>The characters are well developed and has some twists to the story.<br/>Kate&apos;s story begins when she finds her mothers diary and finds out she has a twin also she finds out she is half black her father was white and her mother black.<br/>She has to find out what happened to her twin.<br/><br/>Thank you Netgalley the Author and publisher for a chance to read this book.</span>
