<div id="review_1420572408" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1420572408" />
    <a title="Janine Carbone" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/30635471-janine-carbone"><img alt="Janine Carbone" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442975966p2/30635471.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1420572408?book_show_action=true">Oct 19, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Janine Carbone" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Janine Carbone" href="/user/show/30635471-janine-carbone">Janine Carbone</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1420572408" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10491102126416931512">S.J. Francis has created a racially charged story that has blown me away. With one secret piling on top of another, I was left guessing from beginning to end. It was refreshing to see Kate&apos;s strength and determination even while her world, or what she thought was her world, crumbled right before her eyes. A wonderful debut novel leaving me excited to see what this extremely talented author will come up with next.</span>
  <span id="freeText10491102126416931512" style="display:none">S.J. Francis has created a racially charged story that has blown me away. With one secret piling on top of another, I was left guessing from beginning to end. It was refreshing to see Kate's strength and determination even while her world, or what she thought was her world, crumbled right before her eyes. A wonderful debut novel leaving me excited to see what this extremely talented author will come up with next.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10491102126416931512" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
