<span id="freeTextContainer1074744050101940365">Shattered Lies is a book that grabs a hold of you and makes you think. Beautifully written about a subject that is so relevant in this day and age.<br/>Once you pick up this book and start reading the characters grab you and carry you to the Deep South where they wring every emotion out of you before releasing you drained yet hopeful in the end. I got a free copy for giving a fair review. </span>

          </span>
