<div id="review_2205821748" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2205821748" />
    <a title="Ann Keeran" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/52788665-ann-keeran"><img alt="Ann Keeran" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2205821748?book_show_action=true">Dec 06, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ann Keeran" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ann Keeran" href="/user/show/52788665-ann-keeran">Ann Keeran</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/30082617-shattered-lies">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2205821748" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10318917659813000405">A fascinating look at racial relations in Mississippi from the fifties to present. A beautiful narrative that tells of the interaction between two families, one white and one black. Strong female characters dominate the story and their struggles are quite believable. S.J. Francis has written a remarkable story showing how people and relationships evolve.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


